                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860531-17-victim267 t17860531-17-viclabel106"></join>; on the 17th of January last I lost some planes; they were valued at three shillings; I saw them again on the 11th of April; I believe I lost them on the 2d of April; I saw them at the prisoner's door upon a board for sale; the prisoner is a copper-smith; I believe they are here.</p>

               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
